{"tid":912003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【慘烈片曝光】遼寧Audi猛撼小學生 師生遭撞飛5死18傷","createTime":"2018-11-22T10:36:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T14:43:28.000Z","uid":16697,"like":76,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"d1eb6a04b87bc44af58cd1749d2052c43cb31d68","tid":912003,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T10:36:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181122/58944156?fbclid=IwAR3TgG9rpBNH8eHeagpB75Io_JqsK8gQEjjrPsPm17RhBJDW5P4qxpXQeuY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181122%2F58944156%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3TgG9rpBNH8eHeagpB75Io_JqsK8gQEjjrPsPm17RhBJDW5P4qxpXQeuY&d=rPtqwKu4L7zNuShv7ENrVzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=e214941e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181122%2F58944156%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3TgG9rpBNH8eHeagpB75Io_JqsK8gQEjjrPsPm17RhBJDW5P4qxpXQeuY&h=f12d6863\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181122/58944156?fbclid=IwAR3TgG9rpBNH8eHeagpB75Io_JqsK8gQEjjrPsPm17RhBJDW5P4qxpXQeuY</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181122/large/1542868457_8c85.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181122%2Flarge%2F1542868457_8c85.jpg&h=574f5189&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181122/large/1542868455_9c16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181122%2Flarge%2F1542868455_9c16.jpg&h=d4b18aba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（更新：內容）遼寧省葫蘆島市今日中午12時許發生嚴重交通意外，一部奧迪（Audi）A6房車在當地一間小學門前超速失控，撞向正在過馬路的小學生及教師，現場拍攝片段顯示最少10名師生被撞飛倒地，傷者被送到附近醫院搶救。當局公佈事故最少造成5死18傷。<br />\n<br />\n駕駛奧迪房車的司機事後開車不顧而去。目擊者稱，有警車從後追截，並將Audi逼到一處路邊的溝渠，警方上前將這名司機制服，押到附近派出所接受調查。<br />\n<br />\n現場拍攝的閉路電視片段顯示，中午12時許葫蘆島建昌二小門前有大批小學生過馬路，期間往來車輛都有停下，先讓學生過路，但這部黑色Audi房車卻沒有停下，超速過線，直接撞向學生，多人被撞倒之後，Audi卻沒有停下，繼續行駛，逃離現場。<br />\n<br />\n有目擊者則指出，事發後救護車、警車不斷往來，現場地上有一些兒童的鞋子、雜物，還有血迹。當地警方將涉事的路段封閉。"},{"pid":"6121f4cabc7a98ae0c089d019e5aea90f6f9bfba","tid":912003,"uid":16697,"like":34,"dislike":130,"score":-96,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T10:37:22.000Z","msg":"R.I.P.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好撚慘,希望CHILD登仔收下把口"},{"pid":"85631fd35a34ca69684f81a06a443e0612688496","tid":912003,"uid":146376,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T10:39:27.000Z","msg":"個司機都幾冇責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e90a203705652374c3d89d6685f84da24537f7b","tid":912003,"uid":12021,"like":34,"dislike":16,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T10:39:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b0253b1cb5617d813f2feec612578e7a49cafe46","tid":912003,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T10:40:00.000Z","msg":"佢地好似橫過馬路"},{"pid":"04628bf0948983b6985aeb028ebb7a3e27cbc718","tid":912003,"uid":3117,"like":39,"dislike":4,"score":35,"quote":{"pid":"85631fd35a34ca69684f81a06a443e0612688496","tid":912003,"uid":146376,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T10:39:27.000Z","msg":"個司機都幾冇責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T10:40:24.000Z","msg":"咪係 死咁少"},{"pid":"4fdd2dd76bc5d7ab980c63e2d30bc6bd5f98dd91","tid":912003,"uid":158613,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T10:43:23.000Z","msg":"解像度咁低嘅？"},{"pid":"d36c6c963a5d4eaa067492759afdf19c05c956a0","tid":912003,"uid":106247,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T10:44:55.000Z","msg":"可能司機個爸是刁大大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 乜事都無<br />\n仲可以告班師生撞壞佢架車"},{"pid":"39a8ba4046292041ccb558cfefa98b75352d3644","tid":912003,"uid":32511,"like":27,"dislike":8,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTim